cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.CV 

This paper proposes a method for online classification with explicit regularization, which is a common problem in machine learning and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also discusses the generalization error rate and experiments with natural language processing tasks, which suggests a possible fit for cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
